---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-[#6A5AF9] to-[#049fff] py-16">
  <div class="container relative z-10 mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 md:flex-row md:justify-between">
      <div class="max-w-sm">
        <a class="group flex items-center" href="/" aria-label="SurPrice Bot">
          <img
            src="/SPBLogo.svg"
            alt="SurPrice Bot"
            width="246"
            height="64"
            class="h-10 w-auto"
          />
          <span class="ml-3 text-xl font-bold text-white">Sur<span class="text-white/80">Price</span> Bot</span>
        </a>
        <p data-i18n="footer.tagline" class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-white/80">
          Track prices, get Telegram alerts, and buy at the right moment.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://t.me/sur_price_bot/chat"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          data-i18n="hero.cta"
          class="mt-6 inline-flex h-11 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white px-6 text-sm font-bold text-[#049fff] shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:opacity-90"
        >
          Try Now
        </a>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p data-i18n="footer.linksTitle" class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-white/70">
          Quick Links
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <li><a data-i18n="nav.features" class="text-white/85 transition-colors hover:text-white" href="/#features">Features</a></li>
          <li><a data-i18n="nav.pricing" class="text-white/85 transition-colors hover:text-white" href="/#pricing">Pricing</a></li>
          <li><a data-i18n="nav.faq" class="text-white/85 transition-colors hover:text-white" href="/#faq">FAQ</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 border-t border-white/20 pt-6">
      <p data-i18n="limitations.text" class="text-xs leading-5 text-white/60">
        SurPrice Bot tracks prices on product pages, but it doesn't control store pricing
        and can't guarantee a discount will happen. Some sites change their page
        structure, limit automated checks, or temporarily hide the price. In these
        cases the bot may ask you to refresh the tracker or re-add the link.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-white/70">
        © {year} SurPrice Bot. <span data-i18n="footer.rights">All rights reserved.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
